PROC COMPUTAB <CDEC=d><CSPACE=n><CWIDTH=w><DATA=SAS-data-set><FUZZ=value><INITMISS><NOPRINT><NORTR><NOTRANSPOSE><OPTIONS><OUT=SAS-data-set><RTS=n><SUMONLY>;     
